Berkshire Hathaway HS Pinehurst Realty Group/PH

data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home in the Heart of Pinehurst! Nestled in the coveted Lake Pinehurst area, this stunning one-level ranch home is the epitome of comfort, style, and relaxation. Boasting a wood and brick exterior, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is the perfect retreat for those seeking the quintessential Pinehurst lifestyle.Inside, the home welcomes you with warmth and character, featuring a massive brick wood-burning fireplace that sets the tone for cozy gatherings. Enjoy the luxurious feel of brand-new carpeting throughout, providing a soft and comfortable foundation for your daily living.The heart of this home lies in its remodeled kitchen, a culinary haven boasting custom cabinetry, stunning granite countertops, and a suite of modern appliances, including a range, refrigerator, and built-in microwave. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just love to whip up delicious meals, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary adventures.A highlight of this incredible property is the huge sunroom, a versatile space that can be transformed into your own private man cave, a serene home office, or a lively recreation room. With abundant natural light and views of the outdoors, it's a perfect spot to unwind or entertain.The spacious master bedroom suite offers a serene escape with a ceiling fan, walk-in closet, and a master bathroom that exudes luxury. Pamper yourself with a beautifully designed vanity and a stunningly tiled shower - your daily oasis awaits!Two additional guest bedrooms share a well-appointed bathroom, providing comfortable accommodations for family and friends.Private backyard paradise, complete with a sturdy fence to keep your furry friend safe and sound. Gather around the inviting firepit on cool evenings, or soak your cares away in the rejuvenating hot tub under the starry skies. Irrigation. New HVAC 2022. This property is a golfer's paradise, nestled approximately within 1 mile of Pinehurst Golf courses #1, #2, #3, #4, and #5. Additionally, you'll find The Cradle, Members Pool, and Pinehurst Country Club just a stone's throw away. And when you're ready for a change of pace, explore the historic charm of Old Town Pinehurst. Your Pinehurst lifestyle awaits!
